# Windows

Before running terminal commands, check if the active `.code-workspace` file has this settings block:

```json
"settings": {
  "terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows": "Git Bash",
  "terminal.integrated.profiles.windows": {
    "Git Bash": {
      "path": "C:\\Progra~1\\Git\\bin\\bash.exe",
      "icon": "terminal-bash"
    }
  }
}
```

If missing, add it. If no Git Bash installed, direct user to https://git-scm.com/install/windows (free).
